data.description: $30,000 PRICE REDUCTION!!!  Beautifully built and immaculately maintained Avondale in the sought after Village of Sanibel.  Arriving at the home you will admire the mature professional landscaping.  As you approach the house enjoy the covered front porch and glass entry.  Stepping inside be prepared to be wowed.  High ceilings, open floorplan and lots of natural light creates a bright and airy place to call home.  Take a look at the many upgrades like quartz counters, brand new luxury vinyl floors, custom window treatments including electric shades.  Also, notice the enclosed lanai which creates additional indoor climate controlled living space and versatility to the layout.  Take a peak at the totally private master suite, complete with a custom closet and generous master bath.  This home also features two additional bedrooms with closets and brand new luxury vinyl plank flooring.  No carpet in this house.  There is a 2nd full bathroom located near the guest bedrooms for convenience and privacy.  Stepping out into the courtyard you will enjoy the patio area and more beautiful landscaping. The spacious yard and privacy walls create a blank canvas to set up for outdoor living.   Notice the two separate gates to access the courtyard, whether it be for guests or maintenance.  Some additional features this house offers are high end stainless steel appliances, new painted interior and recently painted exterior, quartz counter tops in both kitchen and bathrooms, storm door at entry, custom closets, hall pantry with custom shelving, whole house water filtration and rain gutters.  Equally impressive is the location of this home.  The Village of Sanibel allows for easy access to everything The Villages has to offer including town squares, shopping, golf, restaurants, the list goes on and on.  This is a move in ready, beautiful home in a perfect location.  Take a look at the pictures and please watch the beautiful video. Congratulations, you have just found your perfect Villages home!
